<!DOCTYPE subsection SYSTEM "mingle_help.dtd">
<subsection title="Recently viewed pages section">
    <p>Mingle displays the pages you've viewed most recently in the <sidebar-button>Recently viewed pages</sidebar-button> side bar section, which is visible in the right hand sidebar when viewing any page.</p>
	<screenshot alttext="Recently viewed pages" src="resources/images/wiki_page_recently_viewed_list.png" />
	<p>Click on the <link>page name</link> link to view the corresponding page, or click on the <link>Index of pages</link> link to view a list of all pages in your Mingle project.</p>
</subsection>


